data.body:
## Error Type
Console Error

## Error Message
Encountered two children with the same key, `foolery-53d`. Keys should be unique so that components maintain their identity across updates. Non-unique keys may cause children to be duplicated and/or omitted — the behavior is unsupported and could change in a future version.


    at li (<anonymous>:null:null)
    at <unknown> (src/components/dep-tree.tsx:31:11)
    at Array.map (<anonymous>:null:null)
    at DepTree (src/components/dep-tree.tsx:19:13)
    at BeadDetailPage (src/app/beads/[id]/page.tsx:103:27)

## Code Frame
  29 |         const depType = dep.type ?? dep.dependency_type ?? "depends";
  30 |         return (
> 31 |           <li key={dep.id} className="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
     |           ^
  32 |             <Badge variant="outline">{depType}</Badge>
  33 |             <Link
  34 |               href={`/beads/${linkedId}`}
